* -----------------------------------------------
* EMPVAL   - Employee file validation program
* -----------------------------------------------

  FILE EMPLOYEE EMPDD
  EMP-ID       1   9  A
  EMP-NAME    10  30  A
  EMP-DEPT    40   4  A
  EMP-SALARY  44   7  N  2
  EMP-STATUS  51   1  A

  W
  ERROR-COUNT  N   6     VALUE 0
  ERR-FIELD    A  12     VALUE SPACES
  ERR-MSG      A  40     VALUE SPACES
  RESULT-MSG   A  20     VALUE SPACES

  P
* TODO 1: Define ERRLIST report with TITLE, HEADING, LINE
*         Columns: EMP-ID, ERR-FIELD, ERR-MSG


* TODO 2: Define SUMMARY report for end-of-run totals
*         Include ERROR-COUNT and RESULT-MSG


* TODO 3: Write checks for each of the six fields:
*   - EMP-ID EQ SPACES
*   - EMP-NAME EQ SPACES
*   - EMP-DEPT EQ SPACES
*   - NOT EMP-SALARY NUMERIC
*   - EMP-SALARY LE 0  (only check if numeric)
*   - EMP-STATUS NE 'A' AND EMP-STATUS NE 'T'
*
* For each error: MOVE field-name TO ERR-FIELD
*                 MOVE 'message'  TO ERR-MSG
*                 PRINT ERRLIST
*                 COMPUTE ERROR-COUNT = ERROR-COUNT + 1


* TODO 4: Add LABEL EOF block
*   IF ERROR-COUNT GT 0
*     MOVE 'VALIDATION FAILED' TO RESULT-MSG
*   ELSE
*     MOVE 'VALIDATION PASSED' TO RESULT-MSG
*   END-IF
*   PRINT SUMMARY

